{"type":"text","timestamp":1775843156197,"sessionID":"ses_2878684e2ffezY1s0Ga7zERhoa","part":{"id":"prt_d787fb3fe001vxttLAy1misAsV","messageID":"msg_d787f8e2a001JJodIqtWq3b5KL","sessionID":"ses_2878684e2ffezY1s0Ga7zERhoa","type":"text","text":"Based on my verification, here's the **Quality Gate Report**:\n\n---\n\n## Quality Gate Report\n\n**Spec:** AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量  \n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**检查时间:** 2026-04-11\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\nThe implementation provides the CRD shared types and constants for the AgentCube runtime API (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`). However, **the client-go library described in the spec is NOT implemented**.\n\n---\n\n### Spec Compliance Checklist\n\n| # | Requirement | Status | Code Location | Notes |\n|---|-------------|--------|---------------|-------|\n| 1 | API Group constants (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`) | ✅ | `constants.go:20-30` | APIGroup, APIVersion, FullAPIVersion defined |\n| 2 | Resource Kind constants | ✅ | `constants.go:35-46` | AgentRuntimeKind, CodeInterpreterKind defined |\n| 3 | Resource name constants | ✅ | `constants.go:51-62` | `agentruntimes`, `codeinterpreters` plural names |\n| 4 | Short name constants | ✅ | `constants.go:66-71` | `ar,ars`, `ci,cis` for kubectl |\n| 5 | Category constants | ✅ | `constants.go:75-80` | `agentcube`, `all` categories |\n| 6 | Label/Annotation keys | ✅ | `constants.go:84-134` | Standard Kubernetes + AgentCube custom labels |\n| 7 | Condition reason constants | ✅ | `constants.go:138-191` | Creating, Running, Succeeded, Failed, etc. |\n| 8 | Timeout constants | ✅ | `constants.go:225-248` | TTL, idle, max lifetime defaults |\n| 9 | Port constants | ✅ | `constants.go:252-266` | HTTP/HTTPS/CodeInterpreter ports |\n| 10 | Resource quantity defaults | ✅ | `constants.go:270-281` | CPU/Memory request/limit defaults |\n| 11 | Finalizer constants | ✅ | `constants.go:297-302` | Sandbox and resource cleanup finalizers |\n| 12 | Common types (Phase, Condition, References) | ✅ | `common_types.go` | 12 shared types defined |\n| 13 | AgentRuntime CRD types | ✅ | `agentruntime_types.go` | Spec, Status, Condition types |\n| 14 | CodeInterpreter CRD types | ✅ | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | Spec, Status, Condition types |\n| 15 | API Registration | ✅ | `register.go:25-54` | SchemeGroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme |\n| 16 | Generated DeepCopy | ✅ | `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | All CRD types have DeepCopy methods |\n| 17 | **ClientSet Interface** | ❌ **MISSING** | N/A | `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` not present |\n| 18 | **Typed client (runtime/v1alpha1)** | ❌ **MISSING** | N/A | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/` not present |\n| 19 | **AgentRuntimesGetter/Interface** | ❌ **MISSING** | N/A | REST client methods not implemented |\n| 20 | **CodeInterpretersGetter/Interface** | ❌ **MISSING** | N/A | REST client methods not implemented |\n\n---\n\n### Test Results\n\n| Test File | Tests | Status |\n|-----------|-------|--------|\n| `common_types_test.go` | 18 tests | ✅ PASS |\n| `agentruntime_types_test.go` | 22 tests | ✅ PASS |\n| `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` | 26 tests | ✅ PASS |\n\n**Total: 66 tests passing**\n\n```\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1       0.010s\n```\n\n---\n\n### Build & Lint Verification\n\n| Check | Command | Result |\n|-------|---------|--------|\n| Build | `go build ./...` | ✅ PASS (exit 0) |\n| Test | `go test ./pkg/apis/...` | ✅ PASS (66 tests) |\n| Vet | `go vet ./pkg/apis/...` | ✅ PASS (no issues) |\n\n---\n\n### Coverage Analysis\n\n**Implemented:**\n- ✅ All CRD type definitions (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\n- ✅ All shared types (Phase, Condition, References, Volume configs, etc.)\n- ✅ All constants (API, Resource names, Labels, Timeouts, etc.)\n- ✅ Scheme registration for Kubernetes\n- ✅ Generated DeepCopy functions\n- ✅ Comprehensive unit tests\n\n**Not Implemented (per spec):**\n- ❌ ClientSet interface and struct\n- ❌ Discovery client integration\n- ❌ Typed REST clients (runtime/v1alpha1)\n- ❌ AgentRuntimesGetter with CRUD methods\n- ❌ CodeInterpretersGetter with CRUD methods\n- ❌ Expansion hooks\n\n---\n\n### Conclusion\n\n**The implementation covers the \"CRD shared types and constants\" part of AR-003**, providing:\n- Complete type definitions for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs\n- All required constants for API group, resource naming, and configuration\n- Proper Kubernetes scheme registration\n- Generated DeepCopy methods\n- Comprehensive test coverage\n\n**The client-go library components described in the spec are NOT implemented.** This includes the clientset, typed REST clients, and getter interfaces with CRUD operations.\n\n**Recommendation:** The current implementation is suitable for the CRD type definitions (which would be used by code-generators to create the client-go library), but if the client-go library itself is required, additional implementation work is needed.","time":{"start":1775843156193,"end":1775843156193}}}
